---
title: "auctionCallback (AuctionBidder)"
---
stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    [*] --> q_check_caller: check msg.sender and from
    q_check_caller --> q_error_access: msg.sender != auction OR from != address(this)
    q_error_access --> [*]: revert AccessForbidden
    q_check_caller --> q_decode: authorized caller
    q_decode --> q_execute: calls = abi.decode(data)
    q_execute --> q_approve: _multiCall(calls)
    q_approve --> [*]: forceApprove(assetOut, msg.sender, amountOut)

    note right of q_execute
        INV-001: Only the configured auction contract can trigger callback
        INV-002: from must be this contract (self-initiated bid)
        INV-003: Arbitrary calls executed via _multiCall to source settlement asset
        INV-004: Approval set for exact amountOut after solve execution
    end note
